description:
Yahtzee and JM8 are playing a bit of Black Mesa alongside some of the devs from Crowbar Collective who worked on the game.

Be sure to grab a copy of Black Mesa on Steam --  https://store.steampowered.com/app/362890/Black_Mesa/

Wishlist Crowbar Collective's upcoming game, Rogue Point --  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1843840/Rogue_Point/

description:
This video is brought to you by GameMaker, the free, fast, and easy-to-use 2D game engine that’s helped power modern classics like UFO 50, Antonblast, and Yahtzee’s Starstruck Vagabond – https://opr.as/SecondWind-3

This week on Firelink, KC, Nick, and Marty chat about the recent wave of live-service projects being canceled by PlayStation from studios like Bluepoint and Bend, and also share some early thoughts on the Switch 2 reveal.
